[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":644},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201009\u002F3159624676\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201009\u002F3159624676\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201009\u002F3159624676\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201009\u002F3159624676\u002F":620,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201009\u002F3159624676\u002F":629},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F09\u002Flearn-hexo-26-travis-ci-deploy\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":603,"date":604,"description":18,"extension":605,"lang":606,"meta":607,"navigation":608,"path":609,"readingMinutes":610,"seo":611,"standalone":612,"stem":613,"tags":614,"tldr":617,"updated":617,"url":618,"__hash__":619},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F26-試著學-Hexo-奇淫技巧-自動化部屬-Travis-CI.md","(26) 試著學 Hexo - 奇淫技巧 - 自動化部屬(Travis CI)","3159624676",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":592},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,33,36,45,48,58,62,65,68,75,89,125,128,148,151,156,159,162,165,181,184,187,190,195,198,201,207,210,214,217,223,226,232,235,241,244,250,253,267,273,276,280,287,292,295,523,530,536,539,542,548,558,567,570,588],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來這一篇開始會是一系列的奇淫技巧(怪怪的名詞)，第一篇就先獻給自動化部屬吧。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"自動化部屬",[16,23,24,25,29,30,32],{},"通常我們在寫完一篇文章時都必須輸入 ",[26,27,28],"code",{},"hexo d -g"," 來編譯生成靜態網頁並上傳到 gh-pages，而這個編譯過程其實也會消耗電腦本身的運算，因此我相信你在輸入 ",[26,31,28],{}," 都有感受到電腦突然風扇高速運轉。",[16,34,35],{},"那麼為了解決這個問題，我們就必須藉助 CI\u002FCD，而什麼是 CI\u002FCD 呢？這邊推薦之前的前輩所撰寫的文章",[16,37,38],{},[39,40,44],"a",{"href":41,"rel":42},"https:\u002F\u002Fithelp.ithome.com.tw\u002Farticles\u002F10219083",[43],"nofollow","Day12 什麼是 CICD",[16,46,47],{},"介紹什麼是 CI\u002FCD 並不是本篇的重點，而是如何使用才是重點，因此本篇將會介紹兩種做法，分別是",[49,50,51,55],"ul",{},[52,53,54],"li",{},"Travis CI",[52,56,57],{},"GitHub Actions",[12,59,61],{"id":60},"上傳-hexo-專案","上傳 Hexo 專案",[16,63,64],{},"在準備做後面的 Travis CI or GitHub Action 之前我們必須先將專案上傳到特定的遠端儲存庫，否則後面操作會無法操作唷~",[16,66,67],{},"因此這邊會先建立一個遠端儲存庫是屬於 Travis 專用的",[16,69,70],{},[71,72],"img",{"alt":73,"src":74},"公開儲存庫","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-14%2021.56.43.png",[16,76,77,78,82,83,88],{},"初次上傳的方式很簡單，我這邊就不再次重複說明，如果你對於 Git 指令還是不熟悉的話，可以考慮回顧一下「",[39,79,81],{"href":80},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200925\u002F1602283117\u002F","(12) 試著學 Hexo - 你不能不學的 Git 基本指令","」章節或者是參考「",[39,84,87],{"href":85,"rel":86},"https:\u002F\u002Fw3c.hexschool.com\u002Fgit\u002Fcfdbd310",[43],"Git & GitHub 教學手冊","」，所以我這邊就直接貼上出事上傳的指令快速帶過否則這一篇會很長。",[90,91,97],"pre",{"className":92,"code":93,"language":94,"meta":95,"style":96},"language-c shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","git add .\ngti commit -m 'first'\ngit remote add origin https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fjc-eng\u002FTravis-hexo-project.git\ngit push -u origin master\n","c","d","",[26,98,99,107,113,119],{"__ignoreMap":96},[100,101,104],"span",{"class":102,"line":103},"line",1,[100,105,106],{},"git add .\n",[100,108,110],{"class":102,"line":109},2,[100,111,112],{},"gti commit -m 'first'\n",[100,114,116],{"class":102,"line":115},3,[100,117,118],{},"git remote add origin https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fjc-eng\u002FTravis-hexo-project.git\n",[100,120,122],{"class":102,"line":121},4,[100,123,124],{},"git push -u origin master\n",[16,126,127],{},"基本上之後你新增文章時，就只需要輸入以下就可以了",[90,129,133],{"className":130,"code":131,"language":132,"meta":96,"style":96},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","git add .\ngti commit -m 'first'\ngit push\n","cmd",[26,134,135,139,143],{"__ignoreMap":96},[100,136,137],{"class":102,"line":103},[100,138,106],{},[100,140,141],{"class":102,"line":109},[100,142,112],{},[100,144,145],{"class":102,"line":115},[100,146,147],{},"git push\n",[16,149,150],{},"這邊請確認您的這個儲存庫是像這樣再繼續往下操作唷",[16,152,153],{},[71,154],{"alt":61,"src":155},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-14%2022.02.52.png",[12,157,54],{"id":158},"travis-ci",[16,160,161],{},"Travis CI 相信滿多人都聽過，我們會使用 Travis CI 的 CI（持續整合）來達到自動部署到我們的 gh-pages，而 CI 的運作模式大概是怎樣呢？簡單來講當使用者將程式碼 commit 到遠端儲存庫時，就會被這個程式自動化處理一些事情，舉凡測試、打包甚至是部署等行為。",[16,163,164],{},"而在使用時 Travis CI 必須注意到一件事情就是它有分企業版與非營利版，只需要看網址就可以知道哪一個是企業版與非營利版",[49,166,167,174],{},[52,168,169,173],{},[39,170,171],{"href":171,"rel":172},"https:\u002F\u002Ftravis-ci.org\u002F",[43]," - 非營利版",[52,175,176,180],{},[39,177,178],{"href":178,"rel":179},"https:\u002F\u002Ftravis-ci.com\u002F",[43]," - 企業版",[16,182,183],{},"這兩者有什麼差別呢？以我個人來講我是推薦使用「非營利版」就好，因為是免費的。",[16,185,186],{},"只是唯一缺點是你必須開源你的專案才能夠使用，如果你的專案是 Private，那麼就必須使用企業版，而企業版最大缺點就是前 100 次免費而已，因此當你 100 次使用完畢就必須付費囉~",[16,188,189],{},"因此這邊我將會介紹「非營利版」為主。",[191,192,194],"h3",{"id":193},"travis-ci-非營利版","Travis CI 非營利版",[16,196,197],{},"基本上 Travis CI 是可以使用 GitHub 帳號登入，所以註冊帳號就真的非常沒有什麼直接快速跳過。",[16,199,200],{},"進入到 Travis CI 之後點一下上方 menu 的 setting",[16,202,203],{},[71,204],{"alt":205,"src":206},"setting","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002FRay_-_Profile_-_Travis_CI.png",[16,208,209],{},"接下來我們必須找到剛剛我們建立的「Travis-hexo-project」儲存庫，如果沒看到的話可以按一下左側的「Sync Account」按鈕，這邊主要是確定專案是找得到為主。",[12,211,213],{"id":212},"github-access-token","Github Access Token",[16,215,216],{},"確定可以在 Travis CI 找到專案之後，讓我們回到 GitHub，進入 Github Access Token 頁面，若找不到的人可以直接點下面連結",[16,218,219],{},[39,220,213],{"href":221,"rel":222},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fsettings\u002Ftokens",[43],[16,224,225],{},"進入到 Github Access Token 之後點一下位於右上的 Generate new token 按鈕",[16,227,228],{},[71,229],{"alt":230,"src":231},"Generate new token","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-16%2014.14.57.png",[16,233,234],{},"名稱可以隨你取名，重點是 repo 下的 public_repo，然後再滾到下方儲存產生 token",[16,236,237],{},[71,238],{"alt":239,"src":240},"public_repo","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-16%2014.17.55.png",[16,242,243],{},"當你送出之後你會取得一組 token (綠色框內)麻煩請複製下來(不要外流)",[16,245,246],{},[71,247],{"alt":248,"src":249},"token","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F1600237180965.jpg",[16,251,252],{},"然後這邊回到 Travis CI 找到我們剛剛建立的專案，按一下 setting 進入 setting 畫面，下面會有一個「Environment Variables」欄位填入以下資訊",[49,254,255,261],{},[52,256,257,258],{},"name: ",[26,259,260],{},"GITHUBHEXO_TOKEN",[52,262,263,264],{},"value: ",[26,265,266],{},"剛剛的 token",[16,268,269],{},[71,270],{"alt":271,"src":272},"Environment Variables","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F1600237782375.jpg",[16,274,275],{},"填入完畢後按下 Add 按鈕即可。",[12,277,279],{"id":278},"建立-travisyml","建立 .travis.yml",[16,281,282,283,286],{},"接下來的流程很重要，我們要建立一個檔案是屬於 Travis CI 的設定檔，Travis CI 的運作都會透過該檔案，例如：產生網頁、安裝環境等，因此我們要在 Hexo 的專案下建立一個檔案叫做 ",[26,284,285],{},".travis.yml","(這邊要注意是根目錄哦)",[16,288,289],{},[71,290],{"alt":285,"src":291},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-16%2014.25.20.png",[16,293,294],{},"內容填入要填什麼呢？這邊我直接提供現成的範本給你們，這樣就不用擔心了。",[90,296,300],{"className":297,"code":298,"language":299,"meta":96,"style":96},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","# 設置系統語言環境\nlanguage: node_js\n# 是否需要 sudo 權限\nsudo: false\n# 設置node_js版本\nnode_js:\n  - '12'\n# 設置暫存區塊\ncache:\n  apt: true\n  directories:\n      - node_modules # 不經常變動的資料夾\n# 指定部落格分支，一般來講是 Master，這是在告知當這個分支有 commit 時候就執行部屬指令\nbranches:\n  only:\n    - master\n## 安裝 Hexo-Cli\nbefore_script:\n  - npm install hexo-cli -g  # 安裝 Hexo 環境\n# 清除緩存並執行編譯\nscript:\n  - hexo clean\n  - hexo generate\n## deploy 相關設置\nafter_success:\n  - sed -i'' \"\u002F^ *repo\u002Fs~github\\.com~${GITHUBHEXO_TOKEN}@github.com~\" _config.yml\n  - hexo deploy\n","yml",[26,301,302,308,322,327,338,344,353,362,368,376,387,395,407,413,421,429,438,444,452,463,469,477,485,493,499,507,515],{"__ignoreMap":96},[100,303,304],{"class":102,"line":103},[100,305,307],{"class":306},"sQrFR","# 設置系統語言環境\n",[100,309,310,314,318],{"class":102,"line":109},[100,311,313],{"class":312},"sKpQp","language",[100,315,317],{"class":316},"sMAXC",": ",[100,319,321],{"class":320},"sTRMh","node_js\n",[100,323,324],{"class":102,"line":115},[100,325,326],{"class":306},"# 是否需要 sudo 權限\n",[100,328,329,332,334],{"class":102,"line":121},[100,330,331],{"class":312},"sudo",[100,333,317],{"class":316},[100,335,337],{"class":336},"sCcAr","false\n",[100,339,341],{"class":102,"line":340},5,[100,342,343],{"class":306},"# 設置node_js版本\n",[100,345,347,350],{"class":102,"line":346},6,[100,348,349],{"class":312},"node_js",[100,351,352],{"class":316},":\n",[100,354,356,359],{"class":102,"line":355},7,[100,357,358],{"class":316},"  - ",[100,360,361],{"class":320},"'12'\n",[100,363,365],{"class":102,"line":364},8,[100,366,367],{"class":306},"# 設置暫存區塊\n",[100,369,371,374],{"class":102,"line":370},9,[100,372,373],{"class":312},"cache",[100,375,352],{"class":316},[100,377,379,382,384],{"class":102,"line":378},10,[100,380,381],{"class":312},"  apt",[100,383,317],{"class":316},[100,385,386],{"class":336},"true\n",[100,388,390,393],{"class":102,"line":389},11,[100,391,392],{"class":312},"  directories",[100,394,352],{"class":316},[100,396,398,401,404],{"class":102,"line":397},12,[100,399,400],{"class":316},"      - ",[100,402,403],{"class":320},"node_modules",[100,405,406],{"class":306}," # 不經常變動的資料夾\n",[100,408,410],{"class":102,"line":409},13,[100,411,412],{"class":306},"# 指定部落格分支，一般來講是 Master，這是在告知當這個分支有 commit 時候就執行部屬指令\n",[100,414,416,419],{"class":102,"line":415},14,[100,417,418],{"class":312},"branches",[100,420,352],{"class":316},[100,422,424,427],{"class":102,"line":423},15,[100,425,426],{"class":312},"  only",[100,428,352],{"class":316},[100,430,432,435],{"class":102,"line":431},16,[100,433,434],{"class":316},"    - ",[100,436,437],{"class":320},"master\n",[100,439,441],{"class":102,"line":440},17,[100,442,443],{"class":306},"## 安裝 Hexo-Cli\n",[100,445,447,450],{"class":102,"line":446},18,[100,448,449],{"class":312},"before_script",[100,451,352],{"class":316},[100,453,455,457,460],{"class":102,"line":454},19,[100,456,358],{"class":316},[100,458,459],{"class":320},"npm install hexo-cli -g",[100,461,462],{"class":306},"  # 安裝 Hexo 環境\n",[100,464,466],{"class":102,"line":465},20,[100,467,468],{"class":306},"# 清除緩存並執行編譯\n",[100,470,472,475],{"class":102,"line":471},21,[100,473,474],{"class":312},"script",[100,476,352],{"class":316},[100,478,480,482],{"class":102,"line":479},22,[100,481,358],{"class":316},[100,483,484],{"class":320},"hexo clean\n",[100,486,488,490],{"class":102,"line":487},23,[100,489,358],{"class":316},[100,491,492],{"class":320},"hexo generate\n",[100,494,496],{"class":102,"line":495},24,[100,497,498],{"class":306},"## deploy 相關設置\n",[100,500,502,505],{"class":102,"line":501},25,[100,503,504],{"class":312},"after_success",[100,506,352],{"class":316},[100,508,510,512],{"class":102,"line":509},26,[100,511,358],{"class":316},[100,513,514],{"class":320},"sed -i'' \"\u002F^ *repo\u002Fs~github\\.com~${GITHUBHEXO_TOKEN}@github.com~\" _config.yml\n",[100,516,518,520],{"class":102,"line":517},27,[100,519,358],{"class":316},[100,521,522],{"class":320},"hexo deploy\n",[16,524,525,526,529],{},"接下來你只要新增文章到 Hexo 專案的 GitHub 進去(也就是有 ",[26,527,528],{},"git push"," 行為)，它就會幫你自動部屬囉~",[16,531,532],{},[71,533],{"alt":534,"src":535},"自動部署","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-16%2014.45.53.png",[12,537,538],{"id":538},"補充",[16,540,541],{},"如果你發現你的 Travis CI 不管怎樣都不甩你的話，你可到 setting 上看一下你的專案有沒有啟用",[16,543,544],{},[71,545],{"alt":546,"src":547},"啟用狀態","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-16%2014.58.07.png",[16,549,550,551,554,555,557],{},"最後這個坑算是滿多人會踩到的，也就是你使用 CI 之後你會發現主題無法正常出現，首先你必需打開你的 Hexo 專案到你目前的主題下，然後啟用顯示隱藏資料夾，並刪除主題下的 ",[26,552,553],{},".git"," 資料夾，因為主題都是採用 git clone 下來的，所以本身會有一個 ",[26,556,553],{}," 資料夾，那由於我們已經有上傳過一次，因此會需要輸入以下指令針對資料夾重新加入版本控制",[90,559,561],{"className":130,"code":560,"language":132,"meta":96,"style":96},"git rm -r --cache themes\u002F\n",[26,562,563],{"__ignoreMap":96},[100,564,565],{"class":102,"line":103},[100,566,560],{},[16,568,569],{},"接下來再重新輸入以下指令就可以正常自動部屬囉",[90,571,573],{"className":130,"code":572,"language":132,"meta":96,"style":96},"git add .\ngit commit -m 'fix'\ngit push\n",[26,574,575,579,584],{"__ignoreMap":96},[100,576,577],{"class":102,"line":103},[100,578,106],{},[100,580,581],{"class":102,"line":109},[100,582,583],{},"git commit -m 'fix'\n",[100,585,586],{"class":102,"line":115},[100,587,147],{},[589,590,591],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}",{"title":96,"sea